{"tid":1285650,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"請指教！點樣幫我娘親對付藍絲朋友","createTime":"2019-07-04T15:57:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T17:59:27.000Z","uid":56151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a056288dd842a657054515b7defaf94ccf2ac681","tid":1285650,"uid":56151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T15:57:41.000Z","msg":"是咁的 我娘親係一個和理非 所有遊行集會佢都幾乎會出去 <br />\n就算今次衝擊佢唔認同都好明白我哋嘅心態<br />\n問題就嚟 佢身邊差唔多全部朋友都係藍絲 點樣可以幫到佢說服 <br />\n佢啲朋友由深藍淺藍不等<br />\n<br />\n例子<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我娘親 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />藍絲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啲後生真係好暴力 衝擊立法會<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢哋衝擊係可能唔啱 但係推動佢嘅係邊個？ 係呢個特區政府<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢哋好麻煩 今次應承佢下次一定會繼續要求要更加多嘅嘢 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你講就係？ 我夠話你有200歲你有冇呀？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁今次佢哋嘅要求越來越多！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁政府有冇回應過一個訴求啊？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />早知就唔可以應承佢哋！<br />\n<br />\n我淨係聽左呢幾句 最後我娘親因為唔想嘈交就自己收咗聲 究竟可以點幫佢說服佢班戇鳩朋友"},{"pid":"10411f3e43752ceda45f937f55fbcfab3f753d6a","tid":1285650,"uid":56151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T16:00:00.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講"},{"pid":"f2af375b86bfebbd90e1d3f1ebd6bfde72132033","tid":1285650,"uid":110008,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T16:00:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uSdhcLg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuSdhcLg.gif&h=fffb75cf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"97eae4bc512253102b681e28a2a5e98c5cbd7125","tid":1285650,"uid":11436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T16:02:07.000Z","msg":"對